# 🎓 AZ-104: Microsoft Azure Administrator
## 📅 30-Day Study Plan (45 Minutes/Day)

If you're looking to tackle the **AZ-104 exam** within the next 30 days, this structured study plan is built to help you reach that goal. 

### 🎯 Plan Overview
* **Daily Commitment:** ~45 minutes per day.
* **Structure:** Focused daily topics with at least one dedicated day per week for review, hands-on practice, and mock exams.

---

## 🗺️ Study Plan At A Glance

| Week | Focus Area | Core Topics Covered |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Week 1** | 🔐 Identity & Governance | Microsoft Entra ID, RBAC, Subscriptions, Policies, Storage Accounts |
| **Week 2** | ⚙️ Compute & Networking | VMs, Containers, VNets, NSGs, Load Balancing, Azure Monitor |
| **Week 3** | 💾 Backup, Recovery & Review | Recovery Services Vaults, Site Recovery, Practice Exams |
| **Week 4** | 🛠️ Reinforcement & Hands-On | CLI/PowerShell, Targeted Revisions, Mock Tests, Exam Day |

