## 🗓️ Weekly Breakdown

### 🔹 Week 1: Azure Identity and Governance

<details>
<summary><b>Day 1: Introduction to Azure Administration</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Understand the role of an Azure Administrator
  * Overview of Azure services and the Azure portal
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: AZ-104 Prerequisites](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/paths/az-104-administrator-prerequisites/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 2: Manage Azure Identities</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Create and manage users and groups in Microsoft Entra ID
  * Manage user and group properties
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Manage identities and governance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/paths/az-104-manage-identities-governance/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 3: Manage Access to Azure Resources</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Implement Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
  * Assign roles at different scopes
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Secure resources with RBAC](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/modules/secure-azure-resources-with-rbac/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 4: Manage Azure Subscriptions and Governance</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Implement and manage Azure Policy
  * Configure resource locks and tags
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Manage subscriptions and governance](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/modules/manage-subscriptions-governance/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 5: Review and Practice</b></summary>

* **Activities:** * Review Days 1–4 topics
  * Take relevant practice quizzes
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Practice Assessments](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/credentials/certifications/azure-administrator/practice-assessment/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 6: Implement and Manage Storage Accounts</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Create and configure storage accounts
  * Configure Azure Storage redundancy
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Implement and manage storage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/paths/az-104-manage-storage/)
</details>

<details>
<summary><b>Day 7: Configure Azure Blob and File Storage</b></summary>

* **Topics:** * Create and configure containers in Blob Storage
  * Configure Azure Files and Azure File Sync
* **Resources:** [Microsoft Learn: Configure Azure Blob Storage](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/training/modules/configure-blob-storage/)
</details>

